But grant the whole people are justifiable, with res∣pect to government, reflect on the consequences of the want of government, in the mean time to individuals: reflect on the horrours attending an universal scene of anarchy and outrage. It will be said, perhaps, that in a general struggle between government and the people, it is soon ended;

